---
@version: [2, current]
@description: Create a new cache file.
@lot: string $from, $fn = null, $id = null
@static: 1
@example: |
  // Quick cache
  Cache::set('.\path\to\file.php');

  // Custom cache
  Cache::set('.\path\to\file.php', function($path): array {
      $data = require $path;
      return do_stuff_with_data($data);
  });
@example-note: If `$fn` is not a function, then the cache content will be set based on the `$from` file content.
